Your 90% burn / 10% reward split per action creates aggressive scarcity—net 1 D3X removed from circulation per action—which can drive token value upward if player demand and engagement grow. This mirrors successful elements in projects like Vulcan Forged's $LAVA (50% burn on daily runs, helping stabilize economy across games) and positions D3X as a "store-of-value" within the game.
