Recommendations to Make It Even Better

Add Safeguards: Energy/cooldown systems or skill-based actions to curb spam (e.g., like Axie energy).
Dynamic Rewards: Halve rates every X actions/milestones to extend runway (e.g., start at 0.1, taper to 0.05).
